data.description: Don't mis this opportunity to own a 3/2 family home located in a residential area few blocks from Barry University and Miami Shores. Very nice floor plan with lots  of potential to turn it into your ideal home.  It has a nice cover terrace in the back with a nice back yard with fruit trees. Also it comes with a jacuzzi and over the ground pool for your enjoyment. All information provided is deemed accurate, but not guaranteed and should be independently verified by buyer
